description: The project was to contribute to a measurable reduction of the causes and incidence of Brucellosis in small ruminants, predominantly, sheep and goats, as well as humans in the PTs.

subproject.description: Reducing the incidence of Brucellosis in animal and humans through yearly mass vaccination campaigns and building the public and private institutional, human and physical capacities to control the disease
subproject.title: BRUCELLOSIS CONTROL
